settings.description: Go high up in the skies to Boom Boom's Castle high up in the air! (There's a secret e-Coin hidden in the turnips in the Plains and a 3-up moon also on top of the Plains).
We finish the first world,the next one is in the desert.
The next world is the forest,this level has a e-coin because i like to draw pixel arts,enjoy.
Yes,if you're questioning,i'm arostiguestrom456 but in another account,so mostly of my levels are going to be similar or a remaster from my old levels,in this case from my old 1-2 "the jumping cave"

This level has a secret exit.
the format of these levels are really cool so i'm doing it again
this is basically a harder version of Reversed Peaks
so many fire bros! well, it's not too many, but still! watch your step in this heated nighttime desert level!
The next level is the larry's castle,enjoy.
